# JMartin Construction — required Vercel env vars
#
# Set in Vercel Project Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# 1. In GHL: create a new workflow, trigger = "Inbound Webhook".
#    Save the workflow once to generate the webhook URL, then copy it here.
# 2. In the workflow, add actions:
#       - Find/Create Contact (map first_name, last_name, phone, email)
#       - Send SMS (to the client's owner number — e.g. (406) 544-4492 — with
#         the payload's name + phone + email + message summary)
#       - (Optional) Send Email to client's inbox
#       - (Optional) Add Conversation message so it appears in the inbox

GHL_WEBHOOK_URL=
